_aLatestUpdates._sText: Final version for which I made alot of improvements and added an extra bonus. :)

_aChangeLog.text: Moved bonus away from main map to prevent trigger mixup on certain zonetrigger plugins.
Improved ambient lighting by a tiny bit but lowered overall lightmap.

_aLatestUpdates._sText:
Just a tiny fix version where I moved the bonus away from the main map, due to a few reports of plugins that use trigger_multiples for zoning, ignoring a deny filter.

I made a stripper fix for it, but here's a more permanent fix. :)

_sText:
Surf_frey2 is a part of my more experimental map series where I just slap shit together from what I've learnt from my other projects. 
(But psst, please do not look up frey1, it's not good)

Hard T3 with 2 bonus, not too long but not too short either.
Designed and tested on CSS & MoM 66tick, 150 aa, 3500 maxvel.

CSGO: https://gamebanana.com/maps/212501
